Package C2G8_Project

Class CONFIG

java.lang.Object
C2G8_Project.CONFIG
public final class CONFIG extends Object
This class is designed as a central configuration and takes the place of a config file. Place all system wide configuration settings in this file and it should be referenced throughout the program. All data members should be public static final and have names that clearly indicate the concern
Author:
Jayson Mendoza
